<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.3.5">
<l>uṇari luḷḷañ cuṭumāl viṉaiyēṉ toḻutumeḻu</l>
<l>tuṇari nāḻal naṟumpō tunamcūḻ kuḻalpeytupiṉ</l>
<l>taṇari lāvi taḷaru meṉavaṉ putantāṉiṭam</l>
<l>puṇari yōtam paṇilam maṇiyun tupullāṇiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If I of harsh fate think [of him, my] heart will certainly burn. Arise;</l>
<l>We will worship in Pullāṇi, where mingling waves cast up shells and jewels,</l>
<l>The place of him who gave me love, scattering on my circling curls</l>
<l>Fragrant buds clustering on the tigerclaw bush so that, if he leaves hereafter,</l>
<l rend="indent">my soul will languish.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
